The Charles Henry Wenman papers span 1798-1951. The collection has been arranged into six series, with several series further arranged into subseries. These series are: 
                <emph render="bolditalic">Personal correspondence, 1899-1950</emph>; 
                <emph render="bolditalic">Fish business records, 1947-1951</emph>; 
                <emph render="bolditalic">Wenman business records, 1915-1925</emph>; 
                <emph render="bolditalic">Wenman legal and real estate papers, 1936-1950</emph>; 
                <emph render="bolditalic">Wenman business and personal ledgers, 1843-1947</emph>; 
                <emph render="bolditalic">Wenman personal writings, 1901-1949</emph>; 
                <emph render="bolditalic">McFarland Family photographs, 1944-1947</emph>; and 
                <emph render="bolditalic">Genealogical papers, 1798-1951</emph>.
